{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Raise SEND funding by \u00a310 billion & stop all new SEND reforms",
        "additional_details": "We want the Government to raise SEND funding by \u00a310 billion and halt all new SEND reforms from being introduced.",
        "background": "Every SEN child has a right to a fair education and the right the support, and we are concerned that if funding is not increased and if the new government reforms are introduced, this won\u2019t happen.",
